1316
01:20:09,310 --> 01:20:11,410
It seems like Yamakura...

1317
01:20:11,710 --> 01:20:14,710
You didn't mean "Yamakura", the owner of the teahouse.

1318
01:20:14,810 --> 01:20:16,020
Instead,

1319
01:20:16,160 --> 01:20:17,910
(Yamakura)
you wanted to say "yamakura, the arrow pillow".

1320
01:20:17,910 --> 01:20:21,510
(Yamakura)That is, the second joint of the thumb
at left hand purlicue when shooting an arrow with a bow.

1321
01:20:22,280 --> 01:20:24,710
I think you wanted to say

1322
01:20:24,810 --> 01:20:29,410
it seems like Suzu Chika's yamakura is injured.

1323
01:20:29,910 --> 01:20:34,310
However, only those who practice archery
would know the word "yamakura".

1324
01:20:34,810 --> 01:20:37,710
Besides, Ryuen doesn't know archery,

1325
01:20:37,810 --> 01:20:40,510
and he even mispronounced bow and arrow.

1326
01:20:42,210 --> 01:20:46,110
Ryuen and I used to practice in the same kendo field.

1327
01:20:46,210 --> 01:20:48,210
But one day,

1328
01:20:48,310 --> 01:20:52,110
I learned that there is an ancient school of kendo
called Yoshitsune in Kyoto.

1329
01:20:52,210 --> 01:20:55,310
So I started to study Chronicles of Yoshitsune by myself.

1330
01:20:55,410 --> 01:20:58,310
I left the kendo field two years ago,

1331
01:20:58,510 --> 01:21:01,510
and became the heir of Chronicles of Yoshitsune.

1332
01:21:01,810 --> 01:21:03,810
Benkei's Yoshitsune.

1333
01:21:04,410 --> 01:21:08,610
I wanted to be Yoshitsune more than being Benkei.

1334
01:21:08,710 --> 01:21:10,510
Do you know how much I wanted to be Yoshitsune?

1335
01:21:12,010 --> 01:21:14,910
But the position of Yoshitsune was occupied by the leader.

1336
01:21:15,010 --> 01:21:20,410
I myself, the noblest in the gang, became Benkei.

1337
01:21:20,910 --> 01:21:24,710
If you want to have the Buddha statue to yourself,
