1338
01:21:25,010 --> 01:21:27,410
Yes, but not for selfish desires.

1339
01:21:27,710 --> 01:21:30,610
I will use the money to build a dojo in Kyoto.

1340
01:21:30,710 --> 01:21:33,510
The Chief Priest has always been leading the temple here.

1341
01:21:33,710 --> 01:21:37,010
Even after the temple was abandoned, he has been in charge of it.

1342
01:21:37,410 --> 01:21:40,810
I asked him to let me be the dojo of Yoshitsune.

1343
01:21:41,410 --> 01:21:44,110
But the leader passed away three months ago.

1344
01:21:44,210 --> 01:21:46,010
