01:22:14,110 --> 01:22:16,610
I'll also be able to find buyers of the Buddha statue.

1354
01:22:16,810 --> 01:22:20,910
Thanks to the convenient Internet.

1355
01:22:21,210 --> 01:22:23,710
So, let's stop here.

1356
01:22:23,910 --> 01:22:25,910
Hurry up and hand over the crystal bead.

1357
01:22:26,510 --> 01:22:28,510
