1368
01:23:03,110 --> 01:23:04,510
Toyama, run!

1369
01:23:05,510 --> 01:23:06,310
Heiji!

1370
01:23:24,910 --> 01:23:27,010
They are my beloved apprentices.

1371
01:23:27,110 --> 01:23:28,910
Don't move.

1372
01:23:35,410 --> 01:23:36,110
Heiji!

1373
01:23:40,210 --> 01:23:42,810
Stop it. He is not Heiji!

1374
01:23:51,510 --> 01:23:55,110
