1382
01:24:13,610 --> 01:24:18,410
But the antidote test product of APTX4869 was gone.

1383
01:24:18,610 --> 01:24:23,310
And Paikaru was taken as a cold medicine so

1384
01:24:23,310 --> 01:24:25,810
