1385
01:24:26,110 --> 01:24:28,110
So I suddenly had the idea

1386
01:24:28,510 --> 01:24:32,210
that to take the medicine that brings a severe cold first,

1387
01:24:32,410 --> 01:24:34,710
and then to have Paikaru afterwards,

1388
01:24:35,510 --> 01:24:36,910
