1390
01:24:39,810 --> 01:24:41,610
Then what?

1391
01:24:42,410 --> 01:24:45,310
As I expected, the experiment was very successful.

1392
01:24:45,410 --> 01:24:48,010
Kudo changed back to himself.

1393
01:24:48,410 --> 01:24:51,410
